What Angular Is

- HTML Compiler

<div id="grid"></div>

$("#grid").dataTable({
  url: "/stuff.json",
  columns: []
});

- Custom Elements, Precursor Web Components

<grid url="/stuff.json"></grid>

- Directive

<div ng-app

1. element directives <grid>
2. attribute directives <div ng-app=""
3. class directives <div class="does-something-dynamic">
4. comments <!-- do-some-crazy-thing-in-a-comment -->

- Lifecycle Phases

1. Scan DOM for directives
2. Execute Linking function on each directive
3. Config Phase
4. Run Phase





